data.description: Welcome to your dream home in The Trails at Aspen Ridge! This stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom gem is nestled on a peaceful cul-de-sac, offering the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a versatile flex room on your left, ideal for a home office, study, or playroom. A convenient half bath is nearby for your guests' comfort. Beyond that, the home opens up to an inviting open floor plan. The spacious family room features a cozy gas fireplace, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere for gatherings. The adjacent dining area provides a perfect space for meals and entertaining. The large kitchen is a chef's delight, complete with ample counter space, a pantry for all your storage needs, and easy access to the attached garage for added convenience. Upstairs, you'll find four generously sized bedrooms and a laundry room for your convenience. The primary suite boasts an en-suite bathroom, adding a touch of luxury to your everyday routine. Plus, the primary bedroom's walk-in closet features plenty of natural light with its windows, making it a pleasant space to organize your wardrobe. Outside, you'll fall in love with the super cute front porch, perfect for sipping your morning coffee or enjoying the beautiful Colorado weather. This home is ideally located in a neighborhood that's not only charming but also offers easy access to military bases, the Colorado Springs Airport, and even the Amazon warehouse, making your daily commute a breeze. Don't miss the opportunity to make this wonderful like-new property your new home. Schedule a showing today! Can't see the home in person? Check out the 360 degree virtual walk through tour linked herein.
